  <summary>10/4/2001--Introduced.
Directs the Secretary of Defense to establish and maintain on the Arlington Naval Annex, Virginia, a memorial dedicated to the men and women who lost their lives as a result of the terrorist attack on the Pentagon on September 11, 2001.</summary>
